PN,41201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FSouthampton were found guilty of a
OL,7,F"deplorable" act of putting pressure
OL,8,Fon a junior member of staff to spy on
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough, the EFL has said.
OL,11,FSaints are now under investigation by
OL,12,Fthe Football Association in relation
OL,13,Fto the 'Spygate' scandal which cost
OL,14,Fthem their place in the Championship
OL,15,Fplay-off final.
OL,17,FThe EFL has published its written
OL,18,Freasons for expelling the club from
OL,19,Fthe play-offs and docking them four
OL,20,Fpoints next season.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
