OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FIn the document, the EFL said: "We
OL,7,Fhave concluded that there was, on the
OL,8,Fpart of the Respondent, a contrived
OL,9,Fand determined plan from the top down
OL,10,Fto gain a competitive advantage in
OL,11,Fcompetitions of real significance by
OL,12,Fdeliberate attendance at opposition
OL,13,Ftraining grounds for the purpose of
OL,14,Fobtaining tactical and selection
OL,15,Finformation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,F"It involved far more than innocent
OL,7,Factivity and a particularly deplorable
OL,8,Fapproach in its use of junior members
OL,9,Fof staff to conduct the clandestine
OL,10,Fobservations at the direction of
OL,11,Fsenior personnel. There was
OL,12,Ftransmission and internal
OL,13,Fdissemination and analysis of footage
OL,14,Fand observations.
OL,16,F"The Commission is not persuaded that
OL,17,Fthis is an exceptional case in which
OL,18,Fthere is evidence that no use was made
OL,19,Fof the material and therefore no
OL,20,Fsporting advantage. "
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FThe young intern, it was revealed, had
OL,7,Fspied on Middlesbrough's training
OL,8,Fground on May 7 and also on Oxford,
OL,9,Fbut he declined to participate in
OL,10,Fanother proven incident at Ipswich.
OL,12,FThe intern described to the
OL,13,FIndependent Commission the "pressure
OL,14,Fhe was placed under".
OL,26,@uD@\OUvD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FThe verdict continued: "The Commission
OL,7,Fconsider that the evidence
OL,8,Fdemonstrates that the output of the
OL,9,Fobservations fed into analysis
OL,10,Fconducted by the team, it was
OL,11,Fdiscussed with Mr Eckert and others
OL,12,Fand it was sought so as to inform the
OL,13,Fstrategy for the match.
OL,15,F"Mr Eckert accepted, as he must, that
OL,16,Finformation such as team selection and
OL,17,Finjuries is sensitive information
OL,18,Fwhich a club would wish to keep
OL,19,Fprivate in the build up to a game.
OL,26,@nD@XOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,F"He also accepted that he had
OL,7,Fspecifically authorised the
OL,8,Fobservations to obtain information
OL,9,Fabout formation in the (Oxford)
OL,10,Fincident and about the availability of
OL,11,Fa key player in the (Middlesbrough)
OL,12,Fincident."
OL,14,FThe Commission also dismissed a claim
OL,15,Fby Eckert that he had not found the
OL,16,Finformation gleaned from the spying
OL,17,F"useful".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]yD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FThe EFL concluded: "The integrity of
OL,7,Fthe play-off competition was seriously
OL,8,Fviolated, and the actions of the
OL,9,Frespondent constituted a deliberate
OL,10,Fattempt to obtain an unfair advantage.
OL,12,F"For that reason, charges 1 and 2
OL,13,F(spying on Boro) attract a much more
OL,14,Fserious sanction which in this case
OL,15,Fmust result in expulsion from the
OL,16,Fcompetition.
OL,18,F"We have considered whether a lesser
OL,19,Fsanction would be possible or
OL,20,Fappropriate while achieving the aim of
OL,21,Fthe rule which has been breached.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,F"Were this event to take place during
OL,7,Fthe regular season a points deduction
OL,8,For other sanction could be applied,
OL,9,Fwhich would strip any sporting
OL,10,Fadvantage and achieve the aims of the
OL,11,Frule by making such activities not
OL,12,Fworth the risk.
OL,14,F"In the play-offs, such a position is
OL,15,Fnot possible. Points deductions for
OL,16,Fthe regular season might still be a
OL,17,Frisk worth taking if it enhanced the
OL,18,Fpossibility of promotion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,F"A financial penalty, as proposed by
OL,7,Fthe respondent, would not be effective
OL,8,Fat this stage in the competition since
OL,9,Fthe financial rewards on offer for a
OL,10,Fteam which is promoted to the Premier
OL,11,FLeague through the play-offs would
OL,12,Frender any penalty meaningless.
OL,14,F"Perversely this may act as an
OL,15,Fincentive for clubs to breach (the
OL,16,Fregulations) and pay the fine in an
OL,17,Feffort to increase the chance of
OL,18,Fpromotion."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1779433579
OL,3,CSaints' spygate actions 'deplorable'
OL,4,Csays EFL
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough welcomed Southampton's
OL,7,Fexpulsion, saying the sanction "sends
OL,8,Fout a clear message for the future of
OL,9,Four game regarding sporting integrity
OL,10,Fand conduct".
OL,12,FThe club, beaten by Saints in the semi-
OL,13,Ffinal, face Hull in Saturday's
OL,14,Fshowpiece at Wembley.
OL,16,FEckert's future as Southampton boss is
OL,17,Fnow in major doubt, while reports
OL,18,Fsuggest the Saints' players are
OL,19,Fconsidering legal action against the
OL,20,Fclub.
OL,26,@oD@`OUrD@LO]
